sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Resources Centre Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open resources centre page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query resources with translations/media
    DB-->>LW: Paginated grouped documents
    LW-->>UI: Render table and expandable rows

    User->>UI: Search/filter/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update query/date/page properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query resources with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated paginated result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render resource groups

    User->>UI: Expand/collapse document group
    UI->>LW: Toggle expanded state
    LW-->>UI: Update row visibility
